ğŸ”‘ Benefits of App Engine

- No infra management â†’ just focus on coding.

- Auto-scaling saves cost during low traffic.

- Supports CI/CD pipelines for automated deployments.

- Secure and highly available (Google manages redundancy).

- Easy rollback with versioning.

âš ï¸ Limitations

- Limited flexibility compared to Compute Engine / Kubernetes.

- Vendor lock-in (tightly bound with Google infra).

- Not suitable for apps needing custom OS/kernel level control.

âœ… Summary

